a method for the solution of transportation problems with tall matrices.wa method is presented for the solution of thetransportation problem having a cost matrix with few columns.  the computer implementation of this methodshows it to be very fast and efficient.  application are indicted for the personnel classification problemas well as the classical transportation problem.  an example is worked out in detail.cacm april, dwyer, p. s.galler, b. a.ca jb february ,   : am